Came here on the advice that this was to be the best burger ever!  Place is crowded and very popular.  But, hey, it's Vegas and this has the name of a celebrity chef on it.  Ate at the bar.  Comfortable spot, games on tv's.  Servers professional but not that friendly.   Food was good.  A solid good, but not out of this world.   What else can I say?   Been here, done here.  Would not go out of my way to return.

